If you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed
`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/e-commerce/issues/new?body=module:%20website_sale_charge_payment_fee%0Aversion:%2015.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.

